Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:44.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤中寻觅自我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:01:00.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}在淡波间追寻儚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:18.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}顿足向空深际蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:29.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}包容渺小自我  继续向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:36.18,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}只望与你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:41.90,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}唯有以笑比心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:47.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}只因有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:52.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}心中充满光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:02:05.36,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥遥幽律逾破宙晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:21.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}唯有醉情满溢心间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:44.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみに　試されるたび  少しずつ　強くなってく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:01:00.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ありふれた　毎日の中　夢のつづき　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:18.74,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}歩きつかれて　見上げた空  深く　どこまでも　Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:29.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ちっぽけな自分　抱きしめて  それでも　進んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:36.18,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたに会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:41.90,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}笑顔を伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:47.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:52.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}光が生まれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:02:05.36,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥かなる　優しい調べ  遠い宇宙　越えて届くの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:21.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}胸の奥　かけがえのない  甘い痛み  満ちていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,======================ED======================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:06.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏に流れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}制服の群れに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}逆らうよに　自転車の
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:20.13,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}ペダル　思いきり踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:24.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放課後のグランドの脇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:28.27,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}金網をくぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:33.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年　見つけた　ひまわりは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:38.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年より　誇らしげに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.23,0:24:41.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}空を見上げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:47.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}折れないように　枯れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:50.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}涙に出来たなら
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:57.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明日は何かが変わるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:04.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}雨降る日は　雨に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.80,0:25:09.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}あの　ひまわりみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:13.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}まっすぐ　背を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:20.38,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}今日は揺れていたって、いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:06.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏下  逆行在流动的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}身着制服的人群中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}尽情地  蹬踩着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:20.13,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}自行车的脚踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:24.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放学后  操场边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:28.27,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}钻过铁丝网
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:33.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年发现的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:38.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}比以往还要骄傲地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.23,0:24:41.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:47.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}不屈不挠  不会枯萎地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:50.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}若是放声哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:57.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明天又会变得怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:04.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}下雨的日子  在雨中摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.80,0:25:09.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}就像那朵向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:13.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}挺直了腰杆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:20.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}哪怕今日有所动摇  也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的假日你有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:37.73,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(510,430)\fs29}情书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在听吗  浅羽特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是部长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和伊里野特派员约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先两人一起去看看电影如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是咖啡馆 卡拉OK 宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去哪里就去哪里  你觉得怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用车的话  我家的轻型卡车借给你也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要双人车的话也有超级幼兽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}（Super Cub：本田公司于1958年生产的摩托车）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(214,441)\fs24}tandem
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,441)\fs24}Super Cub
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知故问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了尽快让伊里野特派员加入我们新闻部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而加深彼此关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来  到时候她想要和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要带我们去参观园原基地\N就只是时间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不行的  那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了  我做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.11,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22\fad(0,200)}调查表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么浅羽特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大头目来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大头目？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  浅羽特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  关于今天的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到了执行任务的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋  变态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈叫你快点去吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直之  早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会晚点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去的话就把招牌转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.40,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}无轨道女孩  西行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你要是睡着了我就扁你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说  还真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要预测可能的行程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并事先全部「打扫」一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的Lv3待命是什么时候解除的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点左右吧  早上的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那加奈到底什么时候睡的觉啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子早上六点就已经在那里等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛不阻止她啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是和之前防空壕的时候完全一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拉你过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓  你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是认为实在不行  那就去阻止她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到浅羽过来还有段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈她为什么穿着制服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是校规吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 现在哪里还有那种孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是不想被认为是不良少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  加奈流鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  就算是浅羽也会带着手帕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子们  开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一跟丢了也绝对不要向\N浅羽的虫子发射信号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会被伊里野看穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人在跟踪浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:39.88,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fad(0,300)}无轨道女孩  西行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学生票一张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学生票一张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真巧啊  浅羽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来在我们不知道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个巨大的阴谋正在进行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许早该料到会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假里占据在殿山的不就是他和浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有赶他们走呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么蠢话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  那可是后山的秘密基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了整个夏天  针对谜样的园原基地加以监视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去附近的田地偷西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着热恋中情侣的车子扔鞭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂养野狸  此类的活动丰富不断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都想加入他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人真做了这些事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你知道多少啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来交换情报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就先从你开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显是你拥有的情报量比较少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先听你的会比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨晚开始  哥哥的样子就很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥出门后我搜查了他的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在情报杂志上\N发现他在这个地点和时间上画了圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  连这都不知道就跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个「防空壕事件」的另一个当事人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实况转播
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在浅羽特派员所携带的物品里\N放了一个小型窃听器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影…无聊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.43,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20\fad(200,200)}浅羽的哥哥是\N变(熊)态哥哥！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.43,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs20\fad(200,200)}笨蛋↑       H-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.43,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs20\fad(200,200)}看啊看啊   呀-  浅羽→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了的话就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时就要啵下去啊  浅羽特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了明天  快啵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼  紧紧贴在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  装作不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了要趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊  浅羽特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那个啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到那样的加奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？ 那样子不是在睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  浅羽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么还在看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电影院看电影有什么不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影本来就是次要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然干嘛特地约来\N这种空荡荡又暗濛濛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  上啊  至少在这里也要啵一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆地给她啵下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦  对于浅羽来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}京子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要转头  用余光来看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里望过去十点钟方向\N水前寺就坐在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旁边的人是夕子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有收到通知的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽身上有奇怪的电波源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是水前寺干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就搭回便车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野也常常在上课时打瞌睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道有在打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以晚上睡得比较晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学校有禁止  但还是有很多人在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么不好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  啊  等…再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把放在那边椅子上的包拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话  快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面都放了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨晚开始就有点古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个区域交错着奇怪的秘密通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且伴有强力干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发信源为复数
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上七点左右还一度停止过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了十点通信量又突然激增
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:10:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能在监视两位特派员的并不只有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地也有可取之处嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽夕子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,务必马上退出戏剧部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入我们新闻部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人如果真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水前寺改变座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易加奈醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人开始说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们待得太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们恐怕是在用自己的无线电\N从旁监听由我方窃听器所传出的电波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要在相同频率混入大功率电波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁他们的接收器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  浅羽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务就是盯紧全场动静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打工的话那就没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伊里野能加入我们新闻部的话\N我也会很高兴的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打什么工？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说…我也能行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两手放在水箱上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你扔掉了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转向这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开我  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我把风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…伊里野  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点上车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的机关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了  伊里野特派员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  我要回去  快松手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  看不到…前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了嘛…干什么嘛…那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野特派员身上散发着一些奇特的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她每天早上乘坐公车上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这趟车从見樽车库发车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途径园原基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驶向园原站
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假之前可没有这班公车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她每天必定要打一次电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是在听取情报服务之类东西的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她经常被校内广播叫去办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像极高概率就此早退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是去了哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  掉下去了掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到河里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来在我周围的女性里优秀人才有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到男性成员中的浅羽特派员…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去他似乎知道点什么内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  防空壕一事才过没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  哥哥好H
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他才不是变态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然来这一手  你这家伙在搞什么名堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍无可忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！ 蝴蝶飞踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到这里应该就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要发现一个窃听器就必须全部检查一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不止一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窃听器…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指那个纽扣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  猫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢…猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋…鞋箱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是伊里野你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的鞋箱里放了猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊   那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  并不是在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女孩子动拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对手是女人我也不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼  恶魔  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然周遭都在传言浅羽特派员\N将转校生带进了防空壕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实恰恰相反
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,综合目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽特派员才是被伊里野特派员拉进去的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个胆小鬼施暴未遂的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个说法可信多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥才不是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想要个怎样的哥哥才满足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少说些「我送你」之类的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么！  你这家伙！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有三十分钟左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到里面等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  没事…的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先坐下来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那里…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的脸色还是不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不舒服的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话叫人来接一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正  你也不能回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想…是不是问了不该问的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能答应我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同伴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候内华达的Manta驾驶员共有五名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(212,441)\fs24}Nevada
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（Manta：一种Mobula japonica科的海水软骨鱼。\N此处指特殊战斗机，机型与此类鱼相似）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是五人中的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经记不清是谁提议的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后剩下的四个人决定去坠落地点看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从飞行记录装置上偷出日志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对照着卫星照片找到了坠落地点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后偷偷地从基地里溜了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不久之后水和食物都用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想着自己会不会就要这么死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…带上你们走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道他是怎么看我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寸草不生的沙漠中心有座公园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直蔓延到地平线的荒芜的沙漠中心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那里有一块用混凝土和沥青铺修的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋千  攀登架  跷跷板之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有很多这样的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连油漆都还没干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然连一个小孩的身影都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们几个  谁都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时觉得…我们都是被抛弃的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在活着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能与人相见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能与人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了就会被当作从一开始就不存在一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升机来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被带回了基地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有任何人责备我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要说的就是这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事之前我一直都没跟任何人提过\N  浅羽你是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也不可以告诉别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你约我  却给你添了这么多的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.85,0:22:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还提这个干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野你突然流鼻血倒下又不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:22:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入部申请…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:46.53,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}入部申请\N姓名 伊里野 加奈\N希望加入新闻部\N申请理由\N因为浅羽在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:53.67,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因为浅羽在那里。


